Title: CTS Corporation to Participate in the Baird Conference on Vehicle Technology & Mobility
Description: LISLE, Ill., Sept. 06, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CTS Corporation (NYSE: CTS), announced today that Kieran O’Sullivan, President and Chief Executive Officer, will participate in the Sidoti Small Cap Conference on September 18, 2024, at 4 p.m. (EDT). The conference will be held virtually. You may access a live webcast of the event using this link. More information and access to the event can be found on the Sidoti Conference website. https://sidoti.com/events/september-sidoti-small-cap-virtual-conf
